{"tid":123137,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滙控本港「炒房」　傳今日裁員20人　集團發言人︰不作回應","createTime":"2017-02-16T15:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T01:53:31.000Z","uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d99014a00d96c88825e179f949a13a2f2a6687e9","tid":123137,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/72311?utm_content=bufferd06bd&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F72311%3Futm_content%3Dbufferd06bd%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=2d8eb603\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/72311?utm_content=bufferd06bd&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\n<br />\n滙控（0005）裁員潮未止，最新消息表示，該行今日﹙16日﹚裁減香港俗稱「炒房」的環球銀行及資本市場業務（GBM）員工，估計涉及20人。<br />\n<br />\n主要是支援炒房的IT員工<br />\n<br />\n滙控內部人士向《明報》透露，受影響員工大部份於中環上班，昨晚起陸續收到通知，主要是支援炒房業務的資訊科技部（IT）員工。GBM的IT員工昨日亦開過會，討論未來的資源調配事宜。<br />\n<br />\n《香港經濟日報》今日亦引述消息指出，受影響員工主要是支援GBM的IT員工，部份在家工作（work from home）的員工昨日收到電郵，要求今日回到公司，預料是要收解僱信。報道亦估計，是次裁員與集團希望精簡炒房業務有關。<br />\n<br />\n1月已傳出裁減100名高層員工<br />\n<br />\n滙控回應本報查詢時指，對相關報導不作任何回應。<br />\n<br />\n不過，近年業績一般的滙控早已表明要在2017年底前大力減省開支，務求令集團維持高效率及提高競爭力。今年1月中，外電已傳出滙控旗下「炒房」去年業績欠佳，計劃進行精簡行動，裁減約100名高層員工，但當時未有提及受影響員工的工作地區。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，滙控「炒房」自2015年起已多次傳出裁員消息，去年6月集團新任全球銀行部聯席主管Matthew Westerman上任後不久，已在全球投資銀行部門裁走數十名高層。"},{"pid":"f8e9d0e378ed3ae45baa8c30c56d94c2a4827473","tid":123137,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"公司有咩事IT狗都係首當其衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n向IT狗致敬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d600ce3da16b9b83b788accb64862d5d47ee8d5a","tid":123137,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公司有咩事IT狗都係首當其衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n向IT狗致敬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為it可以outsource"},{"pid":"d45184070e66f30091634d573e571589b23085b8","tid":123137,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"因為it係死物，冇感覺"},{"pid":"b0029f4735d93327f43dfcc60f20e352e0b5f56a","tid":123137,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:05:21.000Z","msg":"腦魔招喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f84c406a7d53d2a9bbe08297883dfda86d87b7","tid":123137,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:53:31.000Z","msg":"支持抄IT狗，再全部contractor"}]}